    <scopecontent id="ref6" encodinganalog="description">
      <p>Handwritten and signed letter dated 1 May 1867. Faraday writes to a Walter White of the "Royal Academy." Faraday states that an "ingot" should be received by White shortly. This Walter White may have been the English author who lived from 1811 to 1893.</p>
    </scopecontent>
